data.description: Brand New Move in ready home which is hard to find at near by Suwanee technology area,  with warranties in NORTHMARK  SUBDIVISION. Excellent location ! 2.9 miles drive to Suwanee Town Center, ALL shopping, Restaurants , Hospital and Entertainment,  6.8 miles to Mall of Georgia,10 minutes drive to GAS Light Arena for all your entertainment . This home features  a large walk out unfinished Basement with plumbing stubbed in for additional space for theater room , bed room bathroom etc. Very private back yard. Have your own cud-de -sac setting  for your children and pets to play  while you sit and relax at your front porch overlooking  beautiful  pool. Guest bedroom and a full bath on main floor  for your guest privacy.  office with built in Granite desk top with a picture window is an ideal situation to work from home while over looking beautiful trees and quiet surrondings. Large master bed room with extra large walki- in closet, double vanities and walk in shower. Upper level laundry room with two additional guest rooms, a full bath and a loft for additional relaxing  sitting room. LOCATION  ABSOLUTELY COULD NOT BE ANY BETTER!   NORTHMARK is well placed in LANIER HIGH SCHOOL DISTRICT !
